commentPostTextItems.html: Bangladesh win by 79 runs and win the series 3-0. Ireland were never in the game, they lost wickets regularly. Neil O'Brien played well for his 70. Tamim Iqbal is the Man-of-the-Match for his wonderful knock of 129. Shahriar Nafees picks up the Man-of-the-Series award.Thanks for being with us, it is bye from all of us here at Cricinfo.

commentTextItems.html: yorker squeezed out to fine leg.
